And I'll just talk you through it.

1472
01:13:38,625 --> 01:13:40,541
So, Jay, can you kiss her?

1473
01:13:45,666 --> 01:13:47,666
And kiss the neck.

1474
01:13:49,958 --> 01:13:51,625
Then the shoulder.

1475
01:13:53,458 --> 01:13:55,875
Daphne, run your hands through his hair.

1476
01:14:00,000 --> 01:14:01,208
[small fart]

1477
01:14:04,083 --> 01:14:05,500
[whispers] I'm sorry.

1478
01:14:07,375 --> 01:14:10,707
- Did you just fart?
- [giggles] Yes!

1479
01:14:10,708 --> 01:14:13,124
[young Jay chuckles]

1480
01:14:13,125 --> 01:14:15,750
- [Daphne] I'm so sorry.
- It's okay. It's fine.

1481
01:14:16,291 --> 01:14:19,625
- So... sorry.
- [giggling]

1482
01:14:20,333 --> 01:14:21,790
Okay, still rolling.

1483
01:14:21,791 --> 01:14:23,708
- [both inhale]
- Okay.

1484
01:14:26,583 --> 01:14:27,541
[director] Neck...

1485
01:14:32,125 --> 01:14:33,208
Hair...

1486
01:14:35,416 --> 01:14:36,416
Shoulder...

1487
01:14:39,416 --> 01:14:40,708
Okay. Cue Eli.

1488
01:14:42,708 --> 01:14:44,750
- [Daphne] Are you asking to be tickled?
- No.

1489
01:14:45,333 --> 01:14:48,374
- He is. Get him!
- Asking to be tickly!

1490
01:14:48,375 --> 01:14:51,332
- And cut. Good.
- [assistant] Okay, Eli.

1491
01:14:51,333 --> 01:14:53,666
- Time to go back to school.
- Can we go again?

1492
01:14:54,166 --> 01:14:55,041
[director] Really?

1493
01:14:55,833 --> 01:14:58,125
- Maybe I had an idea.
- I thought we were great.

1494
01:14:59,250 --> 01:15:00,250
You did?

1495
01:15:04,500 --> 01:15:05,540
[director] Jay wants to go again.

1496
01:15:05,541 --> 01:15:07,790
- Can we beg the tutor?
- [assistant] Yeah.

1497
01:15:07,791 --> 01:15:10,208
[background chatter]

1498
01:15:12,083 --> 01:15:13,082
Ooh.

1499
01:15:13,083 --> 01:15:14,582
- [young Jay] Yeah?
- Very good.

1500
